fXlNJiOYE=/1928x1712/c23dfbb5-6e60-495c-985d-bccae5139f4c--Screenshot_2025-04-07_at_10.47.30_AM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 500px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/TqOKCnLphFvErmS2bibXi0y319A=/768x682/filters:format(webp)/c23dfbb5-6e60-495c-985d-bccae5139f4c--Screenshot_2025-04-07_at_10.47.30_AM.png, https://images.food52.com/-W2mI-2oLSZvXl5oxFNugKCt1r8=/1536x1364/filters:format(webp)/c23dfbb5-6e60-495c-985d-bccae5139f4c--Screenshot_2025-04-07_at_10.47.30_AM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 500px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/nhzgKFMBlJ0Jgb7_suVQUezBJ78=/768x682/c23dfbb5-6e60-495c-985d-bccae5139f4c--Screenshot_2025-04-07_at_10.47.30_AM.png, https://images.food52.com/PDtCquq8K2HCLC9a89gcWL4ik8g=/1536x1364/c23dfbb5-6e60-495c-985d-bccae5139f4c--Screenshot_2025-04-07_at_10.47.30_AM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/yN1_k-PT2QoXb7HyhyUMEab8lzY=/375x333/filters:format(webp)/c23dfbb5-6e60-495c-985d-bccae5139f4c--Screenshot_2025-04-07_at_10.47.30_AM.png, https://images.food52.com/fBAXXrjKohQhQ6oQKpNjDLTJptA=/750x666/filters:format(webp)/c23dfbb5-6e60-495c-985d-bccae5139f4c--Screenshot_2025-04-07_at_10.47.30_AM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003cimg srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/vH2HiCqNiNgwPDp6HWGc2wmLcoo=/375x333/c23dfbb5-6e60-495c-985d-bccae5139f4c--Screenshot_2025-04-07_at_10.47.30_AM.png, https://images.food52.com/VyiyZpD5HuTu41_r6ppcSQOBIzk=/750x666/c23dfbb5-6e60-495c-985d-bccae5139f4c--Screenshot_2025-04-07_at_10.47.30_AM.png 2x\" alt=\"The final product.\" width=\"964\" height=\"856\" data-expand=\"750\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/vH2HiCqNiNgwPDp6HWGc2wmLcoo=/375x333/c23dfbb5-6e60-495c-985d-bccae5139f4c--Screenshot_2025-04-07_at_10.47.30_AM.png, https://images.food52.com/VyiyZpD5HuTu41_r6ppcSQOBIzk=/750x666/c23dfbb5-6e60-495c-985d-bccae5139f4c--Screenshot_2025-04-07_at_10.47.30_AM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cfigcaption\u003e\n          \u003cspan\u003eThe final product.\u003c/span\u003e\n\n          \u003cspan\u003ePhoto by Anna Arriaga\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n              \u003cp\u003eTo assemble the mini cakes, I frosted the tops generously and topped with fresh berries to my liking. This way, I could just have a little taste of the berry Chantilly deliciousness without going all in on a whole cake. I thought it tasted good, but it was not my favorite. Maybe for the true experience, I have to head to Whole Foods and try that latte!\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eWhat other trending recipes do you want to know more about? Let me know below!\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ch3\u003ePopular on Food52\u003c/h3\u003e\n      \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
